<data>
    <story>
        <scene id="0" background="bg.jpg">
            <bgm src="mid-lude.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <cg src="newchapter.png" bg="bg.jpg"></cg>
            <goto goto="10" change="#000000"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="10" background="westCliffWindow.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <text>A story from a long time ago.</text>
            <text remark="next">From when 「Roswell」 was merely a small town next to the Pecos River.</text>
            <remark>
                <p class="article-text-h">注：</p>
                <p class="article-text">罗斯威尔（Roswell）为美国新墨西哥州的一座城市，1947年7月4日，这里发生了一起不明飞行物坠毁事件。</p>
                <p class="article-text">阴谋论者认为，美国政府当时掩盖了事件的真相；他们相信这是一起飞碟坠毁事故，而不是探空气球坠毁事故。</p>
            </remark>
            <text remark="next">From when 「Bikini」 was merely the name of a small Atoll.</text>
            <remark>
                <p class="article-text-h">注：</p>
                <p class="article-text">比基尼环礁（Bikini Atoll）是马绍尔群岛的一组珊瑚礁岛。从1946年起，这里进行了多达20余次的核武器爆炸试验。</p>
                <p class="article-text">“比基尼”是核爆的象征——当某款划时代的泳装设计被时装界推出时，他们顺理成章地借用了这个地理名词。</p>
            </remark>
            <text>From when I was half of my current age.</text>
            <goto goto="20" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="20" background="einHomeSw.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>1946. Zürich, Switzerland.</text>
            <show chara="fatherEmbarraClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="motherSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="motherNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="motherNormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="motherNoFace">A nice man is coming to talk with you today, Lieserl.</speak>
            <speak chara="motherNoFace">He's different from the previous ones―― Try to get along with him.</speak>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="motherNormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="fatherSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fatherNoFace">Don't worry, he said he won't tell you to go back to school and take those boring classes.</speak>
            <speak chara="fatherNoFace">He's a well known expert, different from the others.</speak>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <goto goto="25" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="25" background="westCliffWindow.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>Also, let me clarify.</text>
            <show chara="motherSeriousClose-up" position="center"/>
            <text>This person is my mom. She's a very busy accountant. She's only really at home on Sunday and Christmas.</text>
            <text>A very boring job, don't you think so?</text>
            <show chara="fatherEmbarraClose-up" position="center"/>
            <text>This person is my dad. He's a designer. To be precise, he makes clock hands.</text>
            <text>An even more boring job, right?</text>
            <hide position="center"/>
            <text>Please try to imagine. How hard was it for me, the only person in this family who liked metaphysics.</text>
            <text>Please try to imagine. I stopped going to school and was forced to meet with five different 「psychologist」 over the course of three months.</text>
            <text>Ah... Metaphysics.</text>
            <text>Since I'm talking about back then, I should adjust my thoughts to match my old self.</text>
            <goto goto="30" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="30" background="einRoomSw.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoNameNoFace">Hello there! I'm Carl... Carl Gustav.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">You can call me 「Carl」 or 「Gustav」, I don't mind either.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einBoringLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">「Carl Gustav」... are you supposed to be the King of Sweden?</speak>
            <show chara="einBoringLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Hahaha... people always joke about that.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">...By the way, I heard you were doing some interesting research lately. Would you mind filling me in?</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">...Hm.</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">「This old man won't get it」――</speak>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">―― Is what you're thinking, right?</speak>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">...I think it'll be a good idea to give it a try first.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">One should explore all their options before coming to a conclusion. Don't you agree?</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">I'm not one to brag―― But I had pretty good grades in science at my university.</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einBoringLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einBoringLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">I swear it's true. I excelled the most at Professor Hilbert's class, 『Geometry』.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Then.</speak>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">...What is the maximum number of straight vertical lines that can exist in space?</speak>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Will you please leave if you can't answer correctly?</speak>
            <goto goto="40" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="40" background="westCliffWindow.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>When I thought about it later... I realized that man wasn't an ordinary person.</text>
            <text>I thought that by presenting this problem which answer I could change on the fly I could chase him out.</text>
            <text>――But by the time I opened my mouth and gave him the problem, he had already won.</text>
            <text>At the very least, he was certainly better than the four previous 「professionals」.</text>
            <goto goto="50" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="50" background="einRoomSw.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Orthogonal straight lines...?</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Then you can make any number of vertical lines you want.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">...!</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">There is no limit to the dimension of space. The coordinate axes themselves are already two infinite straight lines.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">――In short, space and straight lines are artificially determined concepts.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einCryLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einCryLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Um... W-What happened?</speak>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einHappyLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einHappyLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">D-Don't look at me with that smirk... I-I am getting fired?</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einHappyLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">No...</speak>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">It's just...</speak>
            <show chara="einCryLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">I-I...</speak>
            <goto goto="60" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="60" background="">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Uwaaaaaaaaa~~~~――</speak>
            <goto goto="65" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="65" background="westCliffWindow.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>Yes, I started bawling uncontrollably.</text>
            <text>「That smart girl」 was reduced to that. If I were to see my young self I won't be able to not make fun of her.</text>
            <text>But... everyone has a moment in their life when they need to let out their intense emotions, right?</text>
            <text>It's not an ugly thing... On the contrary, it's beautiful. A beautiful time engraved in your personal clock of life you can't avoid.</text>
            <text>For some it comes at the age of 18, some others at 80. And in my case... I was 8 years old, that's all.</text>
            <text>Keeping that in mind, he was the only one who managed to keep up with my craziness... he was truly exceptional.</text>
            <goto goto="70" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="70" background="einRoomSw.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">「Given any two polyhedra of equal volume, is it always possible to cut the first into finitely many polyhedral pieces which can be reassembled to yield the second?」.</speak>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einBoringLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">I think we won't make any progress even if we read it for another hour.</speak>
            <show chara="einBoringLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Any particular thoughts?</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">...Silence. I'm thinking.</speak>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Oh... then that means neither you nor me know.</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Let's see the answer!</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSurpriseLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">What!?</speak>
            <show chara="einSurpriseLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Don't want to? We're exploring the unknown, not taking part in a quiz game.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">But...</speak>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Don't feel frustrated. Everyone's imagination has its limits.</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Which is why it's important to learn using your imagination, this way we'll be able to reach amazing sceneries we've never seen before.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einFretfulLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Let's see...</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Define a variable based on the length and diherdral angle of the polyhedron...</speak>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSurpriseLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">...What? Let me see it!</speak>
            <show chara="einSurpriseLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Hey! Don't pull so hard! You're going to break the book!</speak>
            <goto goto="80" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="80" background="westCliffWindow.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>To tell you the truth, from all the time I spent with that old man solving problems this one is the one I remember the most.</text>
            <text>It isn't only because the answer was impressive. When I told Planck about it later――</text>
            <show chara="emmaBlackClose-up" position="center"/>
            <text remark="next">「Huh? He used Hilbert's third problem to test you? Is he insane!?」</text>
            <remark>
                <p class="article-text-h">注：</p>
                <p class="article-text">希尔伯特的23个问题是德国数学家大卫·希尔伯特（David Hilbert）于1900年在巴黎举行的第二届国际数学家大会上演讲时，提出的“当代23道最重要的数学问题”。</p>
                <p class="article-text">“找出两个具有相同底面积和高的四面体，它们不能被分割成两组对应全等的四面体”正是其中的第3问题。</p>
                <br/>
                <p class="article-text">p.s. 23个问题中比较有名的包括：</p>
                <p class="article-text">1.连续统假设</p>
                <p class="article-text">2.算数公理相容性</p>
                <p class="article-text">8.黎曼猜想、哥德巴赫猜想、孪生素数猜想</p>
                <p class="article-text">18.球体的最密排列</p>
            </remark>
            <hide position="center"/>
            <text>――Of course I would remember something like that.</text>
            <text>Ah, you want to know how I knew Planck back then?</text>
            <text>About that...</text>
            <goto goto="100" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="100" background="einHomeSw.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="emmaNormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Everyone, let me introduce you to someone.</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">This is Emma Planck... the youngest physics professor at Princeton University.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="emmaPromiseSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Hi! I'm Emma, Carl's cousin.</speak>
            <show chara="emmaSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">――I don't know if he does it on purpose or not, but he always forgets to mention we're cousins.</speak>
            <show chara="emmaPromiseSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Well, not that I really care~</speak>
            <show chara="emmaPromiseSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Ahaha...</speak>
            <show chara="fatherEmbarraClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="motherSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="motherNoFace">...Cough.</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="right"/>
            <show chara="emmaNormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Err... back to the topic at hand.</speak>
            <show chara="karlNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">After you consulted me about letting your daughter enter college,</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">I got permission and contacted Emma immediately.</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">I think having a young woman like Emma nearby is great for a child's education.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="emmaPromiseSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">And that's not all! I'm very interested in her too!</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">I would love to explore the truth of this universe together with her!</speak>
            <show chara="fatherEmbarraClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="motherNormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="motherNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="emmaPromiseSeriousClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Hahaha... I'm very sorry. When Emma gets excited she forgets her manners.</speak>
            <show chara="fatherSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <show chara="motherNormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <speak chara="fatherNoFace">No, I think that's a good thing... It'll be good for our daughter.</speak>
            <show chara="fatherSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="motherSlyClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="motherNoFace">.....</speak>
            <speak chara="motherNoFace">...I agree as well.</speak>
            <goto goto="110" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="110" background="westCliffWindow.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>If Carl was the one who introduced me to a new world, Emma was my Sailing Master.</text>
            <text>...At some point I started to call her 「Professor Planck」.</text>
            <text>Emma back then... how should I put it, was a woman who didn't show any signs of a 「midlife crisis」.</text>
            <text>A genuine scholar, a genuine beauty. A light that illuminated me like sunshine――</text>
            <text>一We played the piano, we sang songs, we watched the stars at night together.</text>
            <text>I was closer to her... than I was to my real mother.</text>
            <text>...Of course, I don't mean to imply there was something wrong with Carl. This was simply a 「gender advantage」.</text>
            <goto goto="120" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="120" background="einRoomSw.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Carl, are you going back to Germany tomorrow?</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Yeah...</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">This is my last free weekend so I have to return to HQ.</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSurpriseLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">HQ?</speak>
            <show chara="einSurpriseLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">The Mental Health Center of Berlin's Defense Force.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Hehe... so you really were a 「professional」?</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Hahaha... only now you believe me, what a wrong first impression I must have given you.</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Well, it certainly wasn't as good as you thought it was.</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Working on HQ means you're treating soldiers who suffer PTSD from the war?</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Yeah... it's a tough job if you're not a professional.</speak>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Most people are unable to stand the pain coming from others―― Before long they start to feel that way themselves.</speak>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">So what makes a professional different?</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlNormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">A professional looks at people in a different way.</speak>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">They analyze and treat their suffering, but don't project it onto themselves.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">If personal feelings do show up, they need someone else to take care of the patient.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">...So you're handing me over to Emma?</speak>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">...No no, that's not the case at all.</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">First, you're not my patient. I'm not giving you any treatment. And second, Emma is not a psychologist.</speak>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSmileLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Hehehe, seeing your panicking face was funny!</speak>
            <show chara="einSmileLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">...Eh? You were teasing me?</speak>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">You bad kid, prepare yourself!</speak>
            <show chara="karlSlyClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einCryLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Oh no! The old man raised his hand!</speak>
            <show chara="einCryLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">H-Hey! Don't lie!</speak>
            <hide position="left"/>
            <hide position="right"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Come here!</speak>
            <goto goto="130" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="130" background="einHomeSw.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="karlTiredClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Ha... I-I'm tired...</speak>
            <show chara="karlTiredClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">You look young but you have the stamina of an old man.</speak>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlTiredClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">S-Shut up...</speak>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Anyway, Switzerland sure is great...</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">I hate having to return to Berlin!</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einNormalLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="einHappyLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">...Will you come back someday?</speak>
            <show chara="einHappyLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlThinkingClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Yeah, if I can get another vacation.</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSmileLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">I wish you were a little younger.</speak>
            <show chara="einSmileLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Huh?</speak>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einHappyLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">If you were 10 years younger I could pair you with Emma.</speak>
            <show chara="einHappyLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">That's enough!</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">I've had enough of this bad kid!</speak>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einHappyLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Haha...</speak>
            <show chara="einSmileLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Emma said――</speak>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">「Men call others bad, but secretly they themselves want to be the bad ones!」.</speak>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Hey! What are you teaching her, Emma!?</speak>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einHappyLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Hehe... what did you think I was talking about?</speak>
            <show chara="einProvocativeLittleClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="meEinNoFace">Try to become 20 years younger so you can teach me together with Emma!</speak>
            <hide position="left"/>
            <hide position="right"/>
            <show chara="emmaPromiseSmileClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Oh, that sounds nice! Do your best, Carl!</speak>
            <hide position="center"/>
            <show chara="emmaPromiseSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">E-Emma!? When did you――</speak>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="emmaSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">From around 「if only you were 10 years younger...」.</speak>
            <show chara="emmaPromiseSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">I don't mind that you aren't 10 years younger, by the way.</speak>
            <show chara="emmaPromiseSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">W-W-What are you saying!!!!</speak>
            <goto goto="140" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="140" background="westCliffWindow.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>I was still young, but I had a feeling I couldn't shake off.</text>
            <text>「We probably won't see each other again」.</text>
            <text>But I was unable to say it out loud...</text>
            <text>That Summer became the last day of our life together.</text>
            <text>Carl was very busy and had almost no time to rest. And me who was studying under Planck and doing research on the side, can't say I had free time either.</text>
            <text>Everyone thought 「we'll meet again」.</text>
            <text>Until 3 years ago.</text>
            <text>January 1, 1952. The day a Houkai Impact that destroyed an entire city occurred.</text>
            <text>Carl was in Berlin.</text>
            <text>Not anywhere else, but right there in Berlin. In its epicenter.</text>
            <goto goto="150" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="150" background="hotelSw.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="emmaNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Carl... are you going to see another kid on your next break?</speak>
            <show chara="emmaNormalClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Yeah... probably.</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">That girl already found her path in life, hasn't she?</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">There are still so many lost people in the world who need our help.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="emmaSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Hahaha... that's so like you.</speak>
            <show chara="emmaSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlFoolClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">.....</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Later, Emma. I'm leaving.</speak>
            <show chara="karlSmileClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="emmaNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">.....</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Ah, wait a minute.</speak>
            <show chara="emmaNormalClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">What is it?</speak>
            <show chara="karlShameClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="emmaSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">It's nothing big but...</speak>
            <show chara="emmaSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Weren't you in the choir when you were in college?</speak>
            <goto goto="160" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="160" background="hotelSw.jpg">
            <bgm src="12_15_1946.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="emmaBlackClose-up" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Alright, I brought the instruments.</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">I chose the song myself―― I'm sure you know the lyrics.</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">What are you spacing out for? Go get her. That meddlesome girl tried to give us some 「time alone」!</speak>
            <goto goto="170" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="170" background="CG13-1.jpg">
            <bgm src="10_20_londonderry_p.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Oh, Danny Boy, the pipes, the pipes are calling</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">From glen to glen, and down the mountain side,</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">The summer's gone, and all the roses falling,</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">It's you, it's you must go and I must bide.</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">But come ye back when summer's in the meadow,</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Or when the valley's hushed and white with snow,</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">It's I'll be here in sunshine or in shadow,</speak>
            <speak chara="emmaNoFace">Oh, Danny Boy, oh Danny Boy, I love you so!</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">But when ye come, and all the flowers are dying,</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">And I am dead, as dead I well may be,</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">Ye'll come and find the place where I am lying,</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">And kneel and say an "Avé" there for me;</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">And I shall hear, though soft you tread above me,</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">And all my grave will warmer, sweeter be,</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">For you will bend and tell me that you love me,</speak>
            <speak chara="karlNoFace">and I shall sleep in peace until you come to me...</speak>
            <end post="U2FsdGVkX1+xkpSdMeRC3Mean98cjWF96OT3Viw3ijY="/>
        </scene>

    </story>
